description.plain:
Swedish swing-hip hop-rap band from Luleå, in northern Sweden. They visited The Colbert Report and performed their song Äppelknyckarjazz from their debut album with the same name in 2008, and would thereafter became known in many parts of the world. Even though all of their lyrics are in Swedish, they’ve had tours all over the world and with their unique sound people from all over the world appreciate their catchy beats.

The band consists of Johan Rensfeldt (vocals), Anders Rensfeldt (production) and Joakim Nilsson (saxophone).
